The paper discusses Interactive Machine Learning (IML) which involves the interaction between humans and machine learning algorithms. The primary focus of the paper is on visual analytics, which is a subfield of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses various machine learning techniques used in IML, such as classification (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.HC, followed by cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.IR, and cs.CL.
